data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this extremely beautiful custom home with magnificent views of Granite Mountain. Come enjoy this gorgeous home featuring main-level luxury living, breathtaking panoramic views, wonderful craftsmanship with attention to detail, and top-of-the-line finishes and fixtures throughout. You will know this home is for you upon entering through the front doors which open into a fabulous sunk-in living room that boasts Extra tall ceilings and dual glass French doors that capture the stunning views. A cozy gas fireplace makes this room warm and inviting in the winter months.
